Frederick Burton (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederick_Burton_(actor) 0 Frederick Burton (October 20, 1871 – October 23, 1957) was an American actor. He appeared in 122 films between 1914 and 1947. Burton was born in Gosport, Indiana and died in Woodland Hills, Los Angeles.
